---
alwaysApply: false
---

Almost all commands in the monorepo should be executed from the root of the monorepo. For example, installing packages for the `@rccyx/continuum` app:

```
pnpm --filter @rccyx/continuum add @trpc/server @trpc/client @trpc/react-query @trpc/next @tanstack/react-query zod
```
